native.query:
with mart as (
    select *
    from mart.transactions
    where 
        {{id}} and 
        {{confirmed}} and 
        {{created_at}} and 
        {{type}} and 
        {{fiat_currency}} and 
        {{fiat_amount}} and 
        {{card_bin}} and
        {{id}} and
        type_main in('buy', 'sell')
    order by created_at desc 
)

, acq as (
    select distinct 
        ID as oor_id,
        card_number,
        'DECTA__EXCEL_MANUAL_TO_CSV_UNDUPLICATED' as src
    from RAW.DECTA__EXCEL_MANUAL_TO_CSV_UNDUPLICATED
    
    union all
    select distinct 
        null as oor_id,
        hidden_card_number as card_number,
        'FENIGE__DAILY_REPORT_ECOM_UNDUPLICATED' as src
    from RAW.FENIGE__DAILY_REPORT_ECOM_UNDUPLICATED
    
    union all
    select distinct 
        CUSTOM_DATA as oor_id,
        card_num as card_number,
        'TRUSTPAYMENTS__TRU_MON_FRR_PRES_FEES_UNDUPLICATED' as src
    from RAW.TRUSTPAYMENTS__TRU_MON_FRR_PRES_FEES_UNDUPLICATED
    
    union all
    select distinct 
        case 
            when CARD_BRAND = 'ewallet' then ORDER_ID 
            else MERCHANT_ORDER_ID
        end as oor_id,
        card_number as card_number,
        'UNLIMINT__TRANSACTIONS_XLSX_UNDUPLICATED' as src
    from RAW.UNLIMINT__TRANSACTIONS_XLSX_UNDUPLICATED
    union all
    select distinct 
        MERCHANT_ORDER_ID as oor_id,
        card_number as card_number,
        'UNLIMINT__TRANSACTION_REPORT_CSV_UNDUPLICATED' as src
    from RAW.UNLIMINT__TRANSACTION_REPORT_CSV_UNDUPLICATED
    
    union all
    select distinct 
        CLIENT_UNIQUE_ID as oor_id,
        credit_card_last_4_digits as card_number,
        'NUVEI__MOVEMENT_CSV_UNDUPLICATED' as src
    from RAW.NUVEI__MOVEMENT_CSV_UNDUPLICATED
)

, df as (
    select 
        m.user_id,
        m.id,
        m.confirmed,
        m.created_at,
        m.type,
        m.pay_system,
        m.vendor_name,
        m.fiat_currency,
        m.fiat_amount,
        m.card_bin,
        coalesce(
            concat(w.BIN, substring(w.CARD_NUMBER, length(w.CARD_NUMBER) - 9, 10)),
            case 
                when len(acq.card_number) > 4 then acq.card_number
                when len(acq.card_number) = 4 then concat(m.card_bin, '******', acq.card_number)
            end 
        ) as card_mask
    from mart as m
    left join replica.webapp_card_bindings as w 
        on m.card_id = w.card_id 
    left join acq 
        on case 
            when lower(m.vendor_name) in ('nuvei_moneyamber') then m.PARENT_ID
            when lower(m.vendor_name) like '%decta%' then m.VENDOR_ID
            when lower(m.vendor_name) like '%trustpayments_sbc%' then left(m.VENDOR_ID, 9)
            when lower(m.vendor_name) like '%trustpayments%' then m.PARENT_ID
            when lower(m.vendor_name) IN ('vnd_unlimint_moneyswap', 'ngn_unlimint_moneytea', 'pix_unlimint_moneytea') then m.VENDOR_ID
            when lower(m.vendor_name) IN ('cup_unlimint_moneytea', 'mxn_unlimint_moneytea', 'unlimint_moneyswap', 'unlimint_moneytea', 'unlimint_moneyamber', 'unlimint') then m.PARENT_ID
        end = acq.oor_id
)

select 
    df.*
from df 
[[where card_mask = {{card_mask}}]]

with mart as (
    select *
    from mart.fatpay 
    where 
        {{created_at}} and 
        {{currency}} and 
        {{amount}} and 
        {{card_bin}} and 
        {{status_name}} and 
        {{order_id}}
    order by created_at desc
)

, df as (
    select 
        order_id,
        status_name,
        created_at,
        driver_name,
        currency,
        amount,
        card_bin,
        replace(card_number, 'XXXX', '******') as card_mask
    from mart
)

select df.* 
from df
[[where card_mask = {{card_mask}}]]
